BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:Dxu_JpSEguVnF84otDLUF
SUMMARY:Monster Energy AMA Supercross
DTSTAMP:20260214T003543Z
DTSTART:20260214T233000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Monster Energy SMX World Championship showcases the worlds 
	elite off-road motorcycle racers as they clash in high-flying stadium batt
	les packed with speed\, skill\, and intensity. Feel the adrenaline of the 
	Monster Energy AMA Supercross season as stars like Jett Lawrence\, Cooper 
	Webb\, and Haiden Deegan go full throttle toward the coveted championship 
	title. With nonstop action\, electric crowds\, and an atmosphere you have 
	to experience to believe\, there is nothing like seeing it LIVE!\nAll gues
	ts age 2 & older are required to have a ticket. No costumes for guests 14 
	& older. Please monitor the venue website for venue policies\, including h
	ealth and safety protocols\, which are subject to change. All tickets are 
	subject to availability. Prices and Competitors are subject to change. Rac
	e time subject to change Visit SupercrossLive.com for more event info and 
	Ticket Terms and Conditions.
URL:https://www.ticketmaster.com/monster-energy-ama-supercross-seattle-wash
	ington-02-14-2026/event/0F00632396C517C6
LOCATION:Lumen Field\, 800 Occidental Ave S\, Seattle\, WA
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
